<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="12ff8e69-eb02-405e-87ad-153d660ec45e" >

    <p>If you have been hired as an invigilator by a Department/School and are assigned to work an invigilation shift you will be paid for the hours of the shift. Should you be unable to work this assigned shift during the COVID-19 pandemic you will still be paid for the assigned hours of the shift. The inability to work the assigned shift would be a result of illness or the work is no longer available and alternate work cannot be assigned. If you work more than the assigned hours you will be paid for the additional hours worked.</p>
    





