<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="1f13917a-1ccc-4e79-a0f6-aaf815a518b0" >

    <p>If you have been hired as an invigilator by a Department/School by receiving a contract through eHR, you will be paid for the contract hours as indicated in your letter of appointment. Should you be unable to work your contract hours during the COVID-19 pandemic you will still be paid for the contract hours in your letter of appointment. If you are scheduled and work more than the contract hours in your letter of appointment you will be paid for the additional hours worked. The inability to work these additional hours would be a result of illness or the work is no longer available and alternate work cannot be assigned.</p>
    





